## Dependencies
node_modules/
.pnp/
.pnp.*
.yarn/

## Build output
dist/
build/
*.tsbuildinfo

## Phase 23e runtime build cache. The studio esbuilds client modules
## from public/src/ into <pluginRoot>/.runtime-cache/dist/ at boot.
## Never committed; populated on first run, reused on warm boots.
plugins/deskwork-studio/.runtime-cache/

## Runtime / local state
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

## Editors / OS
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

## Worktree-local commit-message scratch file (per .claude/rules/file-handling.md).
## Subagents write multi-line commit messages here, then 'git commit -F' from it.
.git-commit-msg.tmp

## Claude Code local
.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/settings.local.json~
.claude/worktrees/
## Agent memory belongs in ~/.claude/projects/, never committed
/memory/

## Playwright MCP local scratch (screenshots, console logs, page snapshots
## generated during dogfood UX sessions). Never committed.
.playwright-mcp/

## Superpowers brainstorming companion mockups (visual session content).
.superpowers/

## Local dogfood sandbox — a clone of audiocontrol.org used to drive the
## editorial-calendar lifecycle end-to-end against a real-shaped project
## tree. Lives inside this worktree (not a sibling) to avoid confusion
## with other audiocontrol.org worktrees and to keep tool-permission
## scope inside one directory. Never committed.
/.audiocontrol.org/
